HEADWORD: Half-deck
<hw>Half"-deck`</hw> <pr>(-d⟦ecr⟧k`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A shell of the genus <gen>Crepidula</gen>; a
boat shell. See <er>Boat shell</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

